name: Utils Peaks 1.1
description:
This mod pack makes your playing experience more comfortable with cool features.

It includes:
- Improved Time Bar (Modern Version & Boucing)
- Shaking Icons at low health & BF Winning Icon
- Rating Counter
- Adds the Marvelous rating
- Resume Countdown
- Vanilla Combo Numbers
and more!

Mod Pack created by MaxxVoiid :)
